STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Michael TAYLOR, Defendant-Respondent. C-949 September Term 2016
079231 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 1, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005276-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
